        void onDiscoveryRestarted(@NonNull
                          java.util.List<WearableToken> availableDevices)
        Called when the internal BT scan restarts with a list of FightClub wearable tokens discovered during the single scanning iteration. If a device is contained in the list it is most probably currently active and available for pairing Note: The callback will be executed on the original caller's thread.
        Parameters:
        availableDevices - a list of all Radar Pace devices found during the previous BT scan
